== 分割 ==
截角八面體可分割成正中央一個正八面體、其餘每個面切成8三角帳塔，剩餘的部分在分割成6個[[正四角錐|正四角錐]]。<ref>{{cite web | author= Alex Doskey | title= Chapter 5 - Simplest (R)(A)(Q)(T) Toroids of genus p{{=}}1 | url= http://www.doskey.com/polyhedra/Stewart05.html | work= Alexander's Polyhedra | publisher= doskey.com | date= 2006 | accessdate= 2016-01-30 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160204010023/http://www.doskey.com/polyhedra/Stewart05.html | archive-date= 2016-02-04 | dead-url= no }}</ref>

